{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"146903-sahana-bermain-muzik","title":"Sahana Bermain Muzik","description":"Rumah Sahana terlalu sunyi. Bagaimanakah Sahana dapat memeriahkannya? Dia mula membuat muzik sendiri. Mari kita dengar.","language":"Malay","langCode":"ms","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Lydia Aderus"],"illustrators":["Noorain   Ahmed"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/146903-sahana-bermain-muzik"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725481/size3/36bebfc2c6bd04e5fa90fc5082458ae6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/725481/size6/36bebfc2c6bd04e5fa90fc5082458ae6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90574/size6/d0c171f8fd51417f9b185a6b68986e37.jpg","text":"Sahana cuba membaca.\nKenapa bising sangat di taman?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90892/size6/bd59f16e0f2cbe5112db6c88fb30a0e8.jpg","text":"DRRRRRRRRR\nTHUD\nDhum Dhum\nRATATATATT","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90576/size6/68d9dfbc5616923a685f631cc9b0bc4c.jpg","text":"Sahana berasa bosan.\nKenapa rumahnya\nbegitu senyap?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90577/size6/dfc39db9f09a38d2c84c81c5398fabae.jpg","text":"THUMP\nTOK\nTOK\nTOK\nSahana suka bunyi.\nDia suka muzik.\nDia mula memukul segala-galanya dengan tangannya.\nTHUMP","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90578/size6/bac7477c40529e482ff251b6057f2f46.jpg","text":"CLANG\nCHIIINNNGGG\nBANG","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90894/size6/772f21a1b7245cd2cb4265c3f7261dd7.jpg","text":"OWW\nPLOONG\nTANG\nPLING\nDia memukul tangannya\ndengan sudu.\nTING","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90607/size6/7f802a04db777e28b2ade143c34e1d10.jpg","text":"Sahana mengetik gelas satu demi satu.\nBegitu banyak bunyi dihasilkan.\nPING\nTING\nPING\nTING","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90608/size6/cfc6b5852ffc3d38c572e31cc1ce912a.jpg","text":"TING\nSahana mengetik dengan perlahan.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90609/size6/d6a884429709236beee6f854565c8ab4.jpg","text":"TOOONNNNNNGGGG\nSahana mengetuk\ngelas cawan dengan keras.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90610/size6/903f77b30ba5720509662750d8de5ed5.jpg","text":"Sahana menyorongkan semua sudu\nmerentasi barisan-barisan gelas cawan.\nDia mengetuk gelas yang mempunyai banyak air.\nIa berbunyi pht pht pht pht.\nDia mengetuk gelas yang mempunyai air yang sedikit.\nIa berbunyi krrrin krinnn krinnn krinnnnnng!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90611/size6/72edf8405963d9e6c6cb9cc760a79045.jpg","text":"“Saya bermain muzik!” kata Sahana.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/90612/size6/aae953d4436590ba8e32057a196c5759.jpg","text":"Bunyi adalah gelombang yang tidak dapat dilihat di udara yang anda boleh dengar dengan menggunakan telinga.\nSemakin besar atau kuat bunyi itu, semakin tinggi gelombang tersebut.\nSemakin kecil bunyi itu, semakin rendah gelombang tersebut.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":150}}